snippet.title: Meghan/Harry/Madonna/Biden/Amber Heard/Alec Baldwin/Oprah et al win 2021 BAD TASTE AWARDS
snippet.description:
Please sign Lady Colin Campbell's Petition inviting Prince Harry to ask The Queen to put his titles & royal status into abeyance. https://www.change.org/p/the-public-invitation-to-prince-harry-to-request-the-queen-to-put-his-titles-into-abeyance?utm_content=cl_sharecopy_28949031_en-GB%3A8&recruiter=1205195839&utm_source=share_petition&utm_medium=copylink&utm_campaign=share_petition

🇬🇧 Book order https://www.amazon.co.uk/Meghan-Harry-Lady-Colin-Campbell/dp/1916131719
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Queens-Marriage-Lady-Colin-Campbell/dp/1527209849
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/People-Colour-Royals-Colin-Campbell/dp/1916131700
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Real-Diana-Colin-Lady-Campbell/dp/1900850958
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Diana-Private-Princess-Nobody-Knows/dp/0312081804
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Untold-Life-Queen-Elizabeth-Mother/dp/0956803814
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Daughter-Narcissus-Struggle-Narcissistic-Personality/dp/0992816181

In the two hundred and thirty seventh episode Lady Colin Campbell presents the nominees and winners of the 2021 Bad Taste Awards covering 19 separate categories and including such disparate public figures as the Duke and Duchess of Sussex, President Biden, Madonna, Alec and Hilaria Baldwin, Justin Trudeau, Jussie Smollett, President Macron, Nicola Sturgeon, Whoppi Goldberg, Phillip Schofield, Amid Scabies, and Oprah Winfrey amongst others.
